- You provide GUMROAD_WEBHOOK_SECRET, MAILCHIMP_API_KEY, MAILCHIMP_LIST_ID, and IRONEDIT_API_KEY as environment variables.
- You want to send the upsell email via SendGrid (can be swapped for another ESP/API).
